r and director dr joshua makower md mba cofounder and director age  mr rob beck cpa chief financial officer mr mike rider vice president of engineering  operations compensation as of fiscal year  coravin inc key developments coravin inc expands availability of revolutionary wine systems oct   coravin inc has announced expanded availability of the coravin wine system in more than  bed bath  beyond stores and online providing a growing number of wine lovers with access to their favorite wines without ever removing the cork shoppers can find the coravin system online and in stores throughout the united states shoppers can expect to find a range of options at bed bath  beyond as the retailer will be carrying both the brand new coravin model one and the coravin model two both systems utilize proprietary coravin technology to access wine and deliver bestinclass wine preservation the friendly and functional coravin model one priced at  features a lightweight and durable plastic body with bright soft touch grips model two a modern and elegant system in brushed graphite with metal accents is available for  coravin™ expands availability of revolutionary wine systems in more than  bed bath  beyond stores oct   coravin™ inc announced expanded availability of the coravin wine system in more than  bed bath  beyond stores and online providing a growing number of wine lovers with access to their favorite wines without ever removing the cork shoppers can find the coravin system online and in stores throughout the united states coravin which just celebrated its third anniversary provides users with a unique way to not only taste wine  but also share compare and explore each glass like never before the system gives wine enthusiasts the freedom to drink the wines they want while eliminating the pressure to finish a bottle of wine or pour unfinished wine down the drain shoppers can expect to find a range of options at bed bath  beyond as the retailer will be carrying both the brand new 