g it’s nontoxic and perfectly safe to use with wine how many glasses can i access with each coravin capsule each coravin capsule will allow you to pour up to  glasses of wine capsule longevity will vary depending on how you use the coravin system as well as how often and how much you pressurize each bottle how should i store my coravin capsules coravin capsules can be stored anywhere from a kitchen cabinet to wine cellar just be sure the temperature is between ° and ° f ° to ° c feel free to stock up coravin capsules have a long shelf life how do i dispose of empty coravin capsules coravin capsules are made of recyclable steel prior to recycling please contact your local city or town waste management facility for instructions concerning the disposal of empty compressed gas cylinders please do not dispose of unopened capsules read more faqs here   tech specs size and weight length    diameter    weight capsule   ounces gas   grams   pressure  psi   volume  ml water volume   materials capsule recycled steel   gas  pure argon gas   seal synthetic rubber   cap fiberglass reinforced nylon   capsule life each coravin capsule will allow you to pour up to  five ounce glasses of wine   return policy coravin capsules are nonreturnable and nonrefundable   more questions contact us     email us  coravin try coravin for  days riskfree if you don’t love it return it for a full refund learn more club coravin discover a world of special offers and perks that come with being part of the club learn more newsletter sign up for exclusive coravin updates sign up find us company about us coravin news careers sign up for business partner account more club coravin inspiration whats new where to find a special gift for coravin system customers enjoy a free year subscriptionto wine spectator magazinewhile supplies last receive a year subscriptionto wine spectator magazine  value  issues current subscribers subscriptions will automatically be extended by one year please allow  weeks for deliv